[Name] SPICE-VDAgent
[Summary] Spice agent for Linux
[Description] The Spice agent is an optional component for enhancing user experience and performing 
guest-oriented management tasks. For example, the agent injects mouse position and state to the guest when 
using client mouse mode. It also enables you to move cursor freely between guest and client. Other features 
of agent are shared clipboard (copy and paste between guest and host) and aligning guest resolution with 
client when entering fullscreen mode.
